# Blender Point Tracker

This project is a Blender addon that allows you to track points in a video using .

The algorithm used to track poitns in the video is CoTrackerv2 (https://co-tracker.github.io/) or TapTrv2 (https://github.com/IDEA-Research/TAPTR).


